name: Scoff
wikiSummary: Another rudimentary blast of spite and sarcasm.  The lyric "In your eyes, I'm not worth it" reflects upon Cobain's dysfunctional upbringing, while the refrain "Gimme back my alcohol" can be read as a caustic retort to parental fears that a life on the skids was all that lay ahead for the high school dropout.
wikiText:
Another rudimentary blast of spite and sarcasm.  The lyric "In your eyes, I'm not worth it" reflects upon Cobain's dysfunctional upbringing, while the refrain "Gimme back my alcohol" can be read as a caustic retort to parental fears that a life on the skids was all that lay ahead for the high school dropout.
